# Frontend — React + Vite

## Stack

- React 18, Vite 6, Vitest (`todo-frontend` in `frontend/package.json`)
- Run scripts with **npm** (same as `AGENTS.md` / `tech-stack.mdc`)
- API client in `src/api/todos.js`
- Entry: `main.jsx` → `App.jsx`

## Structure

```
frontend/
├── src/
│   ├── api/         # todos.js
│   ├── components/  # AddTodoForm, TodoList, TodoItem
│   ├── App.jsx
│   └── main.jsx
└── index.html
```

## API Client

Uses `fetch` to `/api/todos`. Base URL from `import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL` or `http://localhost:8080`.

## Testing

- Vitest with `@testing-library/react`, `jsdom`
- CI / once: `cd frontend && npm run test`
- Local watch: `cd frontend && npm run test:watch`
